data.description: This charming residence sits on a .22-acre lot, boasting a private side patio, fenced in yard with irrigation well and tool shed. Inside, you will find a neutral color pallet with a farmhouse feel. 3 bedrooms, one and a half bathrooms and a partially finished basement. Laminate floors stretch over your large living room with plenty of area to entertain. The kitchen has newly refinished cabinets, plenty of storage space, laminate countertops, new light fixtures, double oven and the appliances are included. Corner lot, centrally located in John Day, this home is sure to please.
